sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer / IDE
    participant ACP as ACP Server
    participant Agent as Deep Agent
    participant Sandbox as Sandbox Backend
    participant Tool as External Tool / API

    Dev->>ACP: edit request / task
    ACP->>Agent: prompt + editor context
    Agent->>Sandbox: execute code / read files
    Sandbox-->>Agent: stdout, files, artifacts
    Agent->>Tool: optional MCP / API calls
    Tool-->>Agent: results
    Agent-->>ACP: patch / explanation
    ACP-->>Dev: editor update
    Note over Sandbox: code runs in isolated environment
    Note over ACP,Agent: secrets stay outside sandbox
